Steam has launched its 2017 Winter Sale, offering price cuts on thousands of PC games across its store. In addition to discounts on numerous titles, the Steam Winter Sale also sees the return of the Steam Awards. Users can vote for their preferred game across a number of award categories, and a new category will become available every day until 2 January 2018. The Steam Winter Sale will run from 21 December 2017 until 08:00 on Friday 5 January 2018.